Each citizen member shall serve a term of six (6) years, except the initial appointments shall be as follows:
Two (2) appointments shall expire December 31, 1997;
Three (3) appointments shall expire December 31, 1998;
Two (2) appointments shall expire December 31, 1999;
Two (2) appointments shall expire December 31, 2000;
Two (2) appointments shall expire December 31, 2001; and
Two (2) appointments shall expire December 31, 2002.
